{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_01_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 忘れ物を探しに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、{user}さんや\nおはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Howdy‚ {user}-san.\nMornin'‚ y'all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん？　おはようございます\nなんでここに……今日ってレッスンはお休みですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san? Good morning.\nWhat are you doing here? There are no lessons today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.399999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ。でもそれを言うなら\n{user}さんも同じですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ same to you‚\nright‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ～ひょっとしてですけど\n星見プロのレッスン日を間違えたとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ or did you get the date wrong\nfor Hoshimi Productions’ lesson?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、実はうちの子がスタジオに忘れ物をしたので\n探しに来たんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ one of our girls forgot something in the studio‚\nso I came to look for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.99999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが探しに……？\n随分優しいんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You come lookin' for it‚ {user}-san?\nThat's mighty kind of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.099999999999994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "何を忘れはったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did she forget?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "黄色いネズミのヌイグルミです\n今アニメが放送されてるらしいけど、知ってますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A yellow rat doll.\nApparently it’s a character from an anime that’s on TV now. Know it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.990430816014616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、うちは知らんなぁ\nアニメとか詳しくないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope‚ I don’t.\nI don’t know much about anime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.85709748268129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、そうですよね。鈴村さんは\nアニメとか見るようなタイプじゃなさそうですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ of course. Suzumura-san‚ you don’t look\nlike the type to be into anime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.82376414934796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ふうん？\nそんならうちって、どんなタイプに見えてるんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh?\nSo what kind of type do I look like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.590430816014624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（おっとりしてるように見えて意外としたたかな……）\n（そんなこと、面と向かって言える訳がない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She looks mild‚ but she’s surprisingly calculating…)\n(But that’s not something I can say to her face.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.85709748268127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "その様子から察するに、おっとりしてるように見えて\n意外としたたかな性格、とか思ってます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look as if I seem mild-mannered to you‚\nbut actually unexpectedly calculating. Am I right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3904308160146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……\nいや、そうじゃなくて、えーと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nEr‚ that’s not what I think‚ erm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.22376414934793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃなくて～、なんです？\nまさか、答えられへんこと考えてはるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then what is it?\nSurely you can answer‚ can’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.75709748268127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そんなことは……\nそれより鈴村さんは今日はどうしてここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that’s not it…\nAnyway‚ what are you doing here today‚ Suzumura-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.89043081601461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは正直者やなぁ\n話をそらそうとしているのが丸わかりですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so easy to understand‚ {user}-san.\nEveryone can tell you’re trying to change the topic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.19043081601468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "……ま、あまりいじめるのもなんですし\n今日はこれくらいにしておきましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I feel bad about messing with you too much.\nLet’s leave it here for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8570974826813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "た、助かります……それで、鈴村さんは忘れ物とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That’s a relief. So‚ did you maybe also forget anything‚ Suzumura-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2570974826813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うちが忘れ物をねぇ\nうんうん、それで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ me forgettin' somethin'…\nYep‚ go on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.91278891563412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、忘れ物は……\nダンスシューズとかかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erm‚ and maybe you forgot your…\ndance shoes or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.34612224896742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "あ～惜しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.34612224896742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、ほんまはみんなに内緒で\n自主練しに来ただけなんやけどねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ keep this a secret from everyone.\nBut I just came here for some private practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.99612227280923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、それ全然惜しくないですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not close at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.59612227280925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ん～～？\n言われてみればそうかもしれませんなあ、ふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…?\nNow that you say so‚ then maybe it ain't close at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.60641707579305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "ここのレッスン室、空いてる時は特別に\n自主練に使わせてもらってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I’ve asked to use this lesson room for\nprivate practice when it’s free.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4730837424597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか\nじゃあ今から鈴村さんの自主練が見れるってことですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nThen that means I’ll get to watch your private practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.93975040912628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それはずるいですわ\nこの前、沢山見たんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ that’s sly of you.\nYou’ve already seen a lot‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.03975040912613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "それに、星見プロはライバルです\nこれ以上はサービス出来ませんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and Hoshimi Productions is our rival.\nSo I can’t do any more for nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.13975040912612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことより\nすることがあるんと違いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚\ndon’t you have something you should be doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2245989091465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ、ヌイグルミを探しに来たんでした。確か\n更衣室のロッカーに置き忘れたかもしれないって……",
      "translations": {
